http://publicwiki.deltares.nl/display/EAT/How+to+set+up+a+training

Some ways to create, copy or adjust a scenario:
http://publicwiki.deltares.nl/display/EAT/Scenario+editing

Configuration guide:
http://publicwiki.deltares.nl/display/EAT/Scenario+and+Script+database
http://publicwiki.deltares.nl/display/EAT/Application+configuration
http://publicwiki.deltares.nl/display/EAT/Script+configuration

